      <item>
          <title>统计图的曲线插值</title>
          <pubDate>Mon, 13 Nov 2017 20:58:39 +0000</pubDate>
          <author>Unknown</author>
          <link>https://iovxw.net/p/curve-interpolation/</link>
          <guid>https://iovxw.net/p/curve-interpolation/</guid>
          <description>&lt;p&gt;很多程序, 比如各种监视器, 需要实时绘制统计图来将数据直观的展示给用户&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;
